                            img.img-fluid.d-block.mx-auto(src='/assets/img/portfolio/Airbnb Detail Page.png', alt='...')
                            p In this application I used SQL to organize the data in order to allow users to manage scheduling and booking CRUD operations. I then implemented auth routes to limit a users access to certain booking features to give security to the users information.
